## 🎯 Overview

QuizForge is a full-stack web application that transforms traditional academic assessment into an intelligent, data-driven learning experience. Built specifically for engineering institutions under **Visvesvaraya Technological University (VTU)** and aligned with **NBA/NAAC accreditation** requirements.

### What makes it different?

| Feature | QuizForge | Kahoot! | Quizizz | Google Forms |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Dual-Relationship Access Control | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ |
| Bloom's Taxonomy Auto-mapping | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ |
| Program Outcome Attainment | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ |
| AI Cognitive Profiling | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ |
| PDF/DOCX Tri-Modal Intelligence | ✅ | ❌ | Partial | ❌ |
| Live Quiz with Anti-Cheat | ✅ | Partial | Partial | ❌ |
| Subjective AI Grading | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ |

---

## ✨ Features

### 🔐 Authentication & Access Control
- Email/password authentication via Firebase Auth
- Two roles: **Teacher** and **Student**
- **Dual-Relationship Access Control** — quiz visible only when student is (a) connected to teacher AND (b) matches target batch/year
- Teacher code system + invite link for student connections
- Two-step premium signup flow

### 📝 Quiz Builder
- Five question types: **MCQ, Fill-in-Blank, Q&A, Code, Puzzle/Ordering**
- Per-question Bloom's Taxonomy tagging (Remember → Create)
- Per-question Program Outcome mapping (PO1–PO11)
- Quiz settings: time limits, negative marking, shuffling, live mode, target audience

### 🤖 AI Question Generation
Three difficulty control modes:
- **Uniform** — all questions at same difficulty
- **Distribution** — percentage split across difficulty levels
- **Per-Question** — individual difficulty per question

Difficulty framework with auto Bloom's + time mapping:
| Level | Bloom's | Time |
|---|---|---|
| Easy | Remember / Understand | 40s |
| Medium | Apply | 75s |
| Hard | Analyze | 120s |
| Very Hard | Evaluate / Create | 180s |

Each generated question includes: Bloom's justification, PO justification, difficulty justification, syllabus unit, learning objective.

### 📄 Tri-Modal Document Intelligence
Upload PDF or DOCX and choose:
- **Mode A** — Generate new questions from document content
- **Mode B** — Extract existing questions from document
- **Mode C** — Auto-solve questions found in document

Supports PDF (via pdfjs-dist, up to 20 pages) and DOCX (via mammoth.js).

### ⚡ Live Quiz Engine
- Real-time student activity monitoring (Connected / Attempting / Not Started)
- Per-question countdown timer with Start / Pause / Reset
- Live response distribution per answer option
- Teacher-controlled question progression synced to all students instantly
- Student name badges for active participants

### 🔴 Anti-Cheat System
- Tab-switch detection via `visibilitychange` event listener
- Violations logged to Firestore with timestamp
- Warning shown to student after 3 violations
- Anti-cheat log accessible to teacher post-session

### 📊 Learning Intelligence Analytics
The flagship feature — a full **Learning Intelligence Platform**:

**Student 360° Profile (6 tabs):**
| Tab | Content |
|---|---|
| Overview | Key metrics, learning pattern, AI narrative |
| Cognitive | Bloom's radar chart, HOT index, mastery per level |
| Questions | Per-question breakdown with time spent |
| Behavior | Guessing detection, consistency, PO attainment |
| Trends | SVG performance chart, growth metrics |
| Recommendations | Risk-based interventions, weekly study plan |

**Computed Metrics (20+):**
- Accuracy rate, avg time/question, efficiency score
- Learning velocity (improvement delta)
- Consistency score (inverse std deviation)
- Higher-Order Thinking Index
- Difficulty-wise performance
- Subject-wise performance
- Risk level (High / Medium / Low)

**Question Intelligence:**
- Difficulty Index (p-value)
- Discrimination Index (top 27% vs bottom 27%)
- Distractor analysis with option selection bars
- Quality flags: Too Easy, Too Difficult, Low Discrimination, High Skip Rate

### 🎓 PO Attainment Dashboard (NBA-Compliant)
- PO attainment heatmap with NBA 3-level scale (Level 0–3)
- CO-PO matrix table
- Trends view per PO
- PDF export for NAAC/NBA accreditation submission

### 🧠 Cognitive Profile
- Per-student Bloom's mastery bars
- PO attainment grid
- Learning velocity indicator
- Adaptive next-difficulty recommendation
- AI-generated narrative insight

### 🧩 Crossword Builder
- LLM generates domain-specific clue-answer pairs
- Constraint-satisfaction placement algorithm with adjacency conflict checks
- Interactive keyboard navigation
- Real-time correctness validation (green/red/yellow)
- Click-clue-to-navigate functionality

### 🏆 Other Features
- Global and quiz-specific leaderboards
- AI grading for Q&A and Code answers (score out of 10 + feedback)
- Results page with animated score circle
- Teacher-to-student announcements
- Quiz Apps page (15 external learning tools)
- Dark mode

