## 🛠 Tech Stack

### Frontend
| Technology | Version | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| React | 18.0 | UI framework |
| Vite | 6.0 | Build tool |
| React Router | 6.0 | Client-side routing |
| Zustand | 4.0 | State management |
| Tailwind CSS | 3.0 | Utility-first styling |
| @dnd-kit | 6.0 | Drag-and-drop (puzzle questions) |
| jsPDF | 2.0 | PDF export |
| mammoth | latest | DOCX text extraction |
| pdfjs-dist | latest | PDF text extraction |

### Backend (Firebase BaaS)
| Service | Purpose |
|---|---|
| Firebase Auth | User authentication & session management |
| Cloud Firestore | NoSQL document database |
| Firebase Security Rules | Database-level access control |

### AI Providers
| Provider | Model | Role |
|---|---|---|
| Groq | LLaMA-3.3-70B | Default — fast & free |
| Google Gemini | gemini-2.0-flash | Alternate |
| OpenAI | GPT-4o Mini | Alternate |

### Deployment
| Service | Purpose |
|---|---|
| Vercel | Frontend hosting with global CDN |
| Firebase | Auth + Firestore on Google Cloud |

