## 📜 Patent Innovations <a name="patent"></a>

QuizForge contains **6 patentable innovation clusters** filed under the India Patents Act 1970:

**Cluster 1 — Dual-Relationship Academic Intelligence Engine**
Novel access control enforcing simultaneous connection + batch/year verification.

**Cluster 2 — Adaptive Cognitive Profiling Engine**
Per-student fingerprint across 6 Bloom's levels + 11 POs with learning velocity and adaptive difficulty.

**Cluster 3 — Tri-Modal Document Intelligence Pipeline**
Single pipeline: PDF/DOCX → Mode A (generate) / Mode B (extract) / Mode C (solve).

**Cluster 4 — Synchronized Live Assessment Engine**
Bidirectional real-time quiz with teacher timer control, live response distribution, and tab-switch anti-cheat.

**Cluster 5 — Automated PO Attainment Measurement System**
NBA-compliant CO-PO matrix auto-generated from quiz attempt data.

**Cluster 6 — AI-Crossword Academic Puzzle Engine**
LLM clue generation + constraint-satisfaction grid placement with real-time validation.

